"x disk device info /dev/sdb"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Disk tool with device management and mount/unmount operations:\n- \"x disk\" (default = sum): hardware info + filesystem usage table, all in one view\n- \"x disk info\": static disk hardware info (model, capacity, SMART, etc.)\n- \"x disk stat\": compact filesystem usage table, grouped by physical disk,\n  with APFS container deduplication on macOS\n- \"x disk ls\": compact tabular partition listing (diskutil list / lsblk)\n- \"x disk eject [target]\": eject removable media (USB drives, optical discs)\n- \"x disk mount <device> <mountpoint>\": mount a device to a directory\n- \"x disk umount <mountpoint>\": unmount a mounted filesystem\n- \"x disk remount <mountpoint> <options>\": remount with different options\n- \"x disk device [ls|info]\": list or inspect available devices\nCross-platform with TTY color support and --tsv output for stat.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"磁盘工具，包含设备管理和挂载/卸载操作：\n- \"x disk\"（默认 = sum）：硬件信息 + 文件系统使用率表格，一次看全\n- \"x disk info\"：磁盘硬件信息（型号、容量、SMART 等）\n- \"x disk stat\"：紧凑的文件系统使用率表格，按物理磁盘分组，\n  macOS 上自动合并 APFS 容器\n- \"x disk ls\"：紧凑表格分区列表（diskutil list / lsblk）\n- \"x disk eject [target]\"：弹出可移动介质（U盘、光盘等）\n- \"x disk mount <设备> <挂载点>\"：挂载设备到指定目录\n- \"x disk umount <挂载点>\"：卸载已挂载的文件系统\n- \"x disk remount <挂载点> <选项>\"：以不同选项重新挂载\n- \"x disk device [ls|info]\"：列出或检查可用设备\n跨平台统一输出格式，支持 TTY 彩色输出和 --tsv 机器可读格式。\n"
}
,
"#subcmd:Option"
:
[
"-h"
,
"--help"
]
,
"sum"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
""
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Default subcommand (same as running bare \"x disk\").\nShows physical disk hardware info, then a filesystem usage table\ngrouped by physical disk. Clear section headers separate the two.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"默认子命令（等同于直接运行 \"x disk\"）。\n先显示物理磁盘硬件信息，再显示按物理磁盘分组的文件系统使用率表格。\n有清晰的分段标题。\n"
}
}
,
"info"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"[-s|--simple] [--fresh]"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Show static disk/volume hardware information only — no usage stats.\nmacOS data sources are cached via \"x ccmd 1d\" for speed.\nUse --fresh to force a cache refresh (sets cache duration to 0s).\nDefault (without --simple) shows all fields:\n  physical disk: device, model, revision, serial, capacity, TRIM support,\n    SMART status, partition map, detachable, removable\nWith --simple: only device, model, revision, capacity.\nCache: macOS system_profiler/diskutil cached 1d; Linux /sys no cache needed.\nData sources:\n  macOS — system_profiler SPNVMeDataType/SPSerialATADataType\n  Linux — /sys/block (zero deps) with lsblk fallback\n  Windows — wmic diskdrive\n"
,
"cn"
:
"仅显示静态磁盘硬件信息——不含使用率统计。\n默认（不加 --simple）显示全部字段：\n  物理磁盘：设备、型号、固件版本、序列号、容量、TRIM 支持、\n    SMART 状态、分区表、可拆卸、可移动\n加 --simple：仅显示设备、型号、固件版本、容量。\n数据来源：\n  macOS — system_profiler SPNVMeDataType/SPSerialATADataType\n  Linux — /sys/block（零依赖），lsblk 作为后备\n  Windows — wmic diskdrive\n"
}
}
,
"stat"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"[--tsv|-t]"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Show filesystem usage in compact table format, grouped by physical disk.\nOn macOS: uses diskutil to get APFS container-level data, deduplicates\nvolumes sharing the same container into one row. Picks the best mount\npoint (prefers / then /System/Volumes/Data). Other volumes shown on\nthe next line.\nOn Linux: uses df -Th, merges same-device mounts.\nWith --tsv: outputs tab-separated values for scripting.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"紧凑表格格式显示文件系统使用率，按物理磁盘分组。\nmacOS：使用 diskutil 获取 APFS 容器级别数据，自动合并同一容器的卷。\n优先选择最佳挂载点（/ 优先，其次 /System/Volumes/Data）。\n其他卷名显示在下一行。\nLinux：使用 df -Th，合并同一设备的多挂载点。\n加 --tsv：输出制表符分隔值，方便脚本处理。\n"
}
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
""
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Show compact tabular listing of disks and partitions.\nData sources:\n  macOS — diskutil list\n  Linux — lsblk (with fdisk -l fallback)\n  Windows — wmic diskdrive + wmic logicaldisk tables\n"
,
"cn"
:
"显示磁盘和分区的紧凑表格列表。\n数据来源：\n  macOS — diskutil list\n  Linux — lsblk（fdisk -l 作为后备）\n  Windows — wmic diskdrive + wmic logicaldisk 表格\n"
}
}
,
"eject"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"[device-or-mount]"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Eject removable media (USB drives, optical discs, etc.).\nWithout argument: ejects all ejectable/removable disks.\nWith argument: accepts device (/dev/diskN), short name (diskN), or mount path (/Volumes/USB).\nmacOS: uses diskutil eject or Finder AppleScript.\nLinux: uses udisksctl (preferred) or eject command.\nWindows: uses PowerShell WMI Dismount.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"弹出可移动介质（U盘、光盘等）。\n无参数：弹出所有可移动磁盘。\n有参数：接受设备名（/dev/diskN）、短名（diskN）或挂载路径（/Volumes/USB）。\nmacOS：使用 diskutil eject 或 Finder AppleScript。\nLinux：使用 udisksctl（优先）或 eject 命令。\nWindows：使用 PowerShell WMI Dismount。\n"
}
}
,
"mount"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"<device> <mountpoint> [--options opts]"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Mount a device to a mount point directory.\nAccepts device path (like /dev/sdb1, /dev/disk3s1), UUID, or LABEL.\nCreates mount point if it doesn't exist.\nOptions (Linux): rw, ro, noexec, nosuid, nodev, etc.\nmacOS: uses diskutil mount, options limited (usually rw/ro).\nLinux: uses mount command or udisksctl (user-friendly).\nWindows: mount points are drive letters (C:, D: etc), this subcommand is a no-op.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"挂载设备到挂载点目录。\n接受设备路径（如 /dev/sdb1, /dev/disk3s1）、UUID 或 LABEL。\n挂载点不存在时会自动创建。\n选项（Linux）：rw、ro、noexec、nosuid、nodev 等。\nmacOS：使用 diskutil mount，选项有限（通常只有 rw/ro）。\nLinux：使用 mount 命令或 udisksctl（对用户更友好）。\nWindows：挂载点是驱动器号（C:、D: 等），此子命令无操作。\n"
}
}
,
"umount"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"<mountpoint|--lazy|--force>"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Unmount a mounted filesystem.\nAccepts mount point path or device path.\n--lazy: detach even if busy (Linux: -l)\n--force: force unmount (macOS: diskutil unmount force, Linux: umount -f)\nLinux: also accepts device path without mount point.\nmacOS: requires mount point path.\nWindows: uses PowerShell Dismount for drive letters.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"卸载已挂载的文件系统。\n接受挂载点路径或设备路径。\n--lazy：即使忙碌也强行分离（Linux：-l）\n--force：强制卸载（macOS：diskutil unmount force，Linux：umount -f）\nLinux：也可以接受没有挂载点的设备路径。\nmacOS：需要挂载点路径。\nWindows：为驱动器号使用 PowerShell Dismount。\n"
}
}
,
"remount"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"<mountpoint> <options>"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Remount a filesystem with different options.\nSyntax: x disk remount /mnt/usb ro  (read-only)\n        x disk remount /mnt/usb rw  (read-write)\nLinux: uses mount -o remount,<options> <mountpoint>\nmacOS: limited options, mostly rw/ro via diskutil\nWindows: not applicable\n"
,
"cn"
:
"以不同选项重新挂载文件系统。\n语法：x disk remount /mnt/usb ro  (只读)\n      x disk remount /mnt/usb rw  (读写)\nLinux：使用 mount -o remount,<options> <mountpoint>\nmacOS：选项有限，主要通过 diskutil 支持 rw/ro\nWindows：不适用\n"
}
}
,
"device"
:
{
"#synopsis"
:
"ls|info <device>"
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"List or inspect available block devices.\n\"x disk device ls\" or \"x disk device list\": show all devices with their mount status\n\"x disk device info /dev/sdb\": detailed device info (partition table, UUID, LABEL, etc.)\nLinux: uses lsblk and blkid\nmacOS: uses diskutil list and diskutil info\nWindows: uses wmic diskdrive and wmic logicaldisk\n"
,
"cn"
:
"列出或检查可用块设备。\n\"x disk device ls\" 或 \"x disk device list\"：显示所有设备及其挂载状态\n\"x disk device info /dev/sdb\"：设备详细信息（分区表、UUID、LABEL 等）\nLinux：使用 lsblk 和 blkid\nmacOS：使用 diskutil list 和 diskutil info\nWindows：使用 wmic diskdrive 和 wmic logicaldisk\n"
}
}
,
